ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAdditions to the Metepenagiag Mi’kmaq Nation as Metepenagiag Uta’nk (New Brunswick)
PrecisOrder setting apart 1.146 hectares (2.83 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the METEPENAGIAG MI’KMAQ NATION as METEPENAGIAG UTA’NK, New Brunswick.
